{"tid":666399,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泥頭車錦田公路越線撞九巴　泥頭車司機送院亡","createTime":"2018-05-16T00:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T02:23:24.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d2830ae6bb1a59f20aa22bdadf16240d709c4e","tid":666399,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T00:01:23.000Z","msg":"【20:50更新】警方將循當時路面的情況、車輛的機件性能及涉案司機當時的身體及精神狀況等3方面進行調查<br />\n【18:22更新】九巴表示意外中車長及兩名乘客受傷，已就意外慰問傷者<br />\n【16:00更新】警方安排拖車以求盡快將現場解封，惟因泥頭車載有大量沙石，連拖車亦斷鏈<br />\n【15:29更新】泥頭車司機送院搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n下午2時許，錦田公路發生嚴重車禍，一部泥頭車沿錦田公路往大埔方向行駛，駛至橫台山附近，突越過雙白線，一部九巴駛至，泥頭車猛撼九巴右車頭，巴士女車長一度被困，由附近的南亞人士協助救出，她頭及手部受傷，車上有兩名非洲裔男乘客亦受傷，俱送院治理；而泥頭車司機則被困車廂內，由救援人員救出，頭部重創，全身浴血，昏迷送院搶救，惜最後不治。妻子驚聞噩耗後趕往醫院，其間一度抱頭痛哭，哭得雙眼通紅。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後安排拖車，但因泥頭車煞車系統被鎖，又載有大量沙石，拖車亦無法負荷重量而斷鏈。據悉，傷重死亡的泥頭車司機姓廖（58歲），持有多種駕駛執照，任職職業司機廿多年，當時他正駕駛泥頭車由屯門內河碼頭運載建築石料前往粉錦公路的一間混凝土廠。<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上就意外交代事件，指現場未有發現九巴及泥頭車的煞車痕，而且當時交通情況暢順，上址又並不是交通黑點，又引述泥頭車司機的家人表示，死者平日的身體狀況健康，所以將就當時路面的情況、車輛的機件性能及涉案司機當時的身體及精神狀況等3方面進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n九巴就錦田公路車禍表示，下午1時40分左右，一架54號九巴在八鄉錦田公路往元朗方向，與一架泥頭車相撞，車長及兩名乘客受傷，九巴已慰問傷者，事件有待警方調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526371671_1f5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526371671_1f5b.jpg&h=a6b92f77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(fb「香港交通突發報料區」群組Ben Ng攝)圓圖為喪命泥頭車司機(張家豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526366086_9148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526366086_9148.jpg&h=e76dfd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴與泥頭車相撞,消防在場營救。(讀者Paul提供)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526366752_95ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526366752_95ed.jpg&h=6564fb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴與泥頭車相撞,兩司機被困九巴車長先被救出送院。(fb「香港突發事故報料區」群組Johnny Fung攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526365991_6f76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526365991_6f76.jpg&h=bc9cfe97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(讀者Paul提供)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526367711_713b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526367711_713b.jpg&h=f3d03376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泥頭車司機全身浴血送院搶救。(張家豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526367410_3fdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526367410_3fdb.jpg&h=c2194286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士男乘客送院治理。(張家豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526366946_4125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526366946_4125.jpg&h=98615a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(fb「香港交通突發報料區」群組Ben Ng攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526368946_17be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526368946_17be.jpg&h=e3dec224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴女車長送院救治。(張家豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526366033_4477.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526366033_4477.jpg&h=786addf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(讀者Paul提供)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526367840_00c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526367840_00c5.jpg&h=15258217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有南亞人士在現場協助女車長。(互聯網)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526368948_a6c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526368948_a6c4.jpg&h=00b39f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴另一名男乘客受傷送院。(張家豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526388759_a151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526388759_a151.jpg&h=47096a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方將循當時路面的情況、車輛的機件性能及涉案司機當時的身體及精神狀況等3方面進行調查。(馬耀文攝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180515/58195181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F58195181&d=pPGJYqMZWzvH3DasdLYL2ZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=4e18e93d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F58195181&h=475d9f78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180515/58195181</a>"},{"pid":"abcffdf94329065351adb8418421aee8200f16cb","tid":666399,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T01:07:50.000Z","msg":"睇個款似恰眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8866f9eeda337b618aad219269ac3cc5ee034a","tid":666399,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"今次真係做泥鬼囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}